data.description: Go right through for 357 Bailey! You will love how this cute home is situated directly across from Bailey Center and park, just a quick walk to downtown East Lansing and all of the MSU events! Inside you will find gorgeous, refinished hardwood floors throughout and 3 bedrooms with a full remodeled bath including granite and tile surround. This home also boasts newer windows and roof and includes a 1 car garage. Enjoy the additional space in the basement which includes all new block windows, epoxy floor, dry bar and an additional full bath. This spectacular house in the most ideal spot will not last long, so schedule your showing today!
